      <title>斯里兰卡左翼政党誓言调整国际货币基金组织协议后赢得大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/sri-lanka-leftist-wins-presidency-after-vowing-to-rejig-imf-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡的左翼候选人赢得了一场竞争激烈的总统选举，选民们因为该国陷入危机的两年间所遭受的经济痛苦而将现任总统赶下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/sri-lanka-leftist-wins-presidency-after-vowing-to-rejig-imf-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 14:18:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对手联手挑战主导地位，美国忧虑加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/us-worries-deepen-as-adversaries-team-up-to-challenge-dominance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数月来，美国一直警告伊朗不要向俄罗斯发射弹道导弹，并要求中国不要为莫斯科的乌克兰战争提供军事部件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/us-worries-deepen-as-adversaries-team-up-to-challenge-dominance</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛伊研究所称中国在亚洲的影响力已低于美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/china-s-power-in-asia-plateauing-below-us-lowy-institute-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据洛伊研究所对亚洲地区影响力的年度分析，由于中国经济实力受到限制，其在亚洲的影响力正稳定在低于美国的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/china-s-power-in-asia-plateauing-below-us-lowy-institute-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士选民否决政府养老金改革方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/swiss-voters-shoot-down-government-s-pension-fund-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士选民否决了政府的一项企业养老金改革计划，这是今年第二次在全民公决中否决了一项旨在使国家退休制度适应人口结构变化的提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/swiss-voters-shoot-down-government-s-pension-fund-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 10:05:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>真主党回应传呼机攻击 以色列北部成为攻击目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/israel-s-north-under-fire-as-hezbollah-responds-to-pager-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，以色列与真主党之间的交火愈演愈烈，总部位于黎巴嫩的真主党向以色列北部大片地区发射了大约 115 枚火箭弹、导弹和无人机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/israel-s-north-under-fire-as-hezbollah-responds-to-pager-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 07:56:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉巴马州警方称伯明翰深夜枪击事件造成四人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/4-killed-in-late-night-shooting-in-birmingham-alabama-police-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉巴马州伯明翰（美联社）——警方周日凌晨表示，在阿拉巴马州伯明翰一个受欢迎的夜生活区，发生大规模枪击事件，造成 4 人死亡，18 人受伤，许多受害者被困在交火中。当局在搜寻枪手时向公众征求线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/4-killed-in-late-night-shooting-in-birmingham-alabama-police-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 07:25:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列突袭并关闭半岛电视台西岸新闻局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/urgent-israel-raids-and-shuts-down-al-jazeera-s-bureau-in-ramallah-in-the-west-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜，阿拉伯联合酋长国（美联社）——周日凌晨，以色列军队突袭了卫星新闻网络半岛电视台位于以色列占领的约旦河西岸的办公室，勒令该电视台关闭。以色列正在扩大针对这家卡塔尔资助的广播公司的行动，因为它报道了加沙地带的以色列与哈马斯战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/urgent-israel-raids-and-shuts-down-al-jazeera-s-bureau-in-ramallah-in-the-west-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 01:58:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡左翼候选人在首次决选中领先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/sri-lanka-leftist-candidate-takes-early-lead-in-election-count</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在斯里兰卡历史上首次总统选举决选中，左翼候选人领先，因为没有任何候选人获得直接获胜所需的 50% 选票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/sri-lanka-leftist-candidate-takes-early-lead-in-election-count</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 00:41:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
